Title: SYSTEM OF A DOWN - ATWA (MUSIC VIDEO) | SFM ANIMATION
Description:
How you see this convict now?

DESCRIPTION:
• In the past 6 years of animating experience, this is my first attempt in making a music video animation. I tried hard in realism, because naturally, I'm not an animator and came in 3D-animation only with the desire to be a DIRECTOR. If I had an ability or a chance of participating in something like this as a director, I'd more likely do so. That's why it's more of a directing and writing kind of work. Although, all the animation was still done by me ( ͡ᵔ ᴗ ͡ᵔ)

• The clip here is made to touch the person watching it. 
Whether you'll have a feeling of injustice, sadness or anger (or any other indescribable feeling), if you feel something and your mood would change, or atleast the video would encourage you to leave a comment (no matter if it's positive or negative), then it would mean that I accomplished what I wanted.

• This is a fan-made animated music video on one of my favorite SOAD songs. The original lyrics doesn't refer to what happens in my video, however, I thought it would be a good idea to use them in this context.
